WEBVTT

00:00:07.250 --> 00:00:11.779
Welcome to your Bible study.

00:00:11.779 --> 00:00:16.780
Millions around the world enjoy this interactive Bible course.

00:00:16.780 --> 00:00:18.780
And we hope you will too.

00:00:18.780 --> 00:00:24.429
What will you learn?

00:00:24.429 --> 00:00:32.229
How to have a happy family life.

00:00:32.229 --> 00:00:34.229
How to cope with anxiety.

00:00:34.229 --> 00:00:41.640
How to draw closer to God.

00:00:41.640 --> 00:00:54.759
And why you can hope for a better future.

00:00:54.759 --> 00:00:58.759
What can you expect during a study session?

00:00:58.759 --> 00:01:02.759
Your teacher may begin the study with a brief prayer.

00:01:02.759 --> 00:01:09.359
Next, you will discuss the first page of the lesson.

00:01:09.359 --> 00:01:14.359
Read a paragraph and then discuss the question for that paragraph.

00:01:14.359 --> 00:01:23.859
Before reading the next, most paragraphs have key Bible verses highlighted.

00:01:23.859 --> 00:01:31.859
Your teacher will also read and discuss with you other verses, especially those marked read.

00:01:31.859 --> 00:01:36.859
Next, read and discuss the section dig deeper.

00:01:36.859 --> 00:01:46.780
By reading scriptures, discussing questions and watching videos that are available to you,

00:01:46.780 --> 00:01:52.780
you will learn more about how the topic of the lesson can help you personally.

00:01:52.780 --> 00:02:01.819
Finally, after reviewing the lesson, your teacher may say a prayer to end the study session.

00:02:01.819 --> 00:02:08.000
How often do you need to have a study session?

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:11.000
And how long should each session last?

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:13.000
This is flexible.

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:21.409
But to maximize the benefits of this course, we recommend covering at least one lesson per week.

00:02:21.409 --> 00:02:30.500
The Bible is the world's best guide to a happy life.

00:02:30.500 --> 00:02:35.500
Discover how it can help you in this interactive Bible course.
